
~~~ 
<h3 id="1">1: Prefix project name with Test.</h3>
~~~
tags: *test, julia*

A test pattern.
~~~
<pre><code class="plaintext">match='name = ":[name]"' 

rewrite='''
name = "Test:[name]"'''
</code></pre>
~~~


~~~ 
<h3 id="2">2: Use ismissing instead of === and !==</h3>
~~~
tags: *julia*

Note that `ismissing` can be slower, see <https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/issues/27681>.
~~~
<pre><code class="plaintext">match=':[[var]] :[first~[=|!]]== missing' 

rule='where rewrite :[first] { "=" -> "" }'

rewrite=':[first]ismissing(:[var])'
</code></pre>
~~~


~~~ 
<h3 id="3">3: Replace Array{T,1} with Vector{T}</h3>
~~~
tags: *julia*

Vector{T} and AbstractVector{T} are aliases for respectively Array{T,1} and AbstractArray{T,1}.
~~~
<pre><code class="plaintext">match='Array{:[T],1}'

rewrite='Vector{:[T]}'
</code></pre>
~~~

